{"tid":471871,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機電池可用時間相差25小時! 消委會報告 15款智能手機測試比拼","createTime":"2017-11-17T16:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T15:12:24.000Z","uid":107023,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a079512b532e934c2382eac987af811b4bb64d71","tid":471871,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"電池表現－ iPhone 8表現平平<br />\n<br />\n都市人生活頻繁，經常使用手機，不少人更要隨身攜帶「尿袋」，所以手機的電池表現當然是測試重點之一。測試發現各樣本充滿電所需時間差異頗大，由1.5至3.5小時不等。於模擬日常使用情況下，電池充滿後可使用時間由18至43小時不等，相差超過1倍。以下是測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n括號內代表：（充滿電可使用時間(小時)／充滿電需要時間(小時)）<br />\n<br />\n1. Samsung Galaxy Note 8：★★★★1/2 （24&middot;5/1.67)<br />\n<br />\n2. Apple iPhone 8 Plus：★★★1/2 （21/3)<br />\n<br />\n3. HTC U11：★★★1/2 (20/2)<br />\n<br />\n4. OnePlus 5：★★★★★ (29/1/5)<br />\n<br />\n5. Sony Xperia XZ Premium：★★★1/2 (19/3)<br />\n<br />\n6. Asus Zenfone 3 Zoom：★★★★★ (43／3.25)<br />\n<br />\n7. Samsung Galaxy J7：★★★★★ (29/2.75)<br />\n<br />\n8. Lenovo Moto E4 Plus：★★★★★(36/3.5)<br />\n<br />\n9. Sony Xperia L1：★★★(18/3.5)<br />\n<br />\n10. Alcatel A3 XL：★★★(19/3.25)<br />\n<br />\n11. Apple iPhone 8：★★★1/2 (19/2.5)<br />\n<br />\n12. Honor 9：★★★★ (23/2.25)<br />\n<br />\n13. Samsung Galaxy J5 ：★★★★★(32/2.25)<br />\n<br />\n14. Nokia 3：★★★1/2 (21/3)<br />\n<br />\n15. Lenovo Moto C Plus：★★★★★ (35/3.5)<br />\n<br />\n當中Sony Xperia L1及Alcatel充滿電分別需約3.5及3.25小時，充滿電的速度較慢，而且充滿電後分別只可用18小時及19小時，故只得3點評分。OnePlus、三星Samsung Galaxy J7 及Galaxy J5不用3小時便能充滿電，One Plus 5及Samsung Galaxy J7可使用29小時，而Asus Zenfone 3 Zoom、Lenovo Moto E4 Plus及Moto C Plus雖然要用超過3小時才充滿電，但充滿電後可使用35小時或以上，亦獲5點評分。<br />\n<br />\n測試結果發現，非常受香港人歡迎的Apple手機電池表現平平，iPhone 8 Plus需3小時充滿電，充滿電後可使用21小時。而iPhone 8 需2.5小時充滿電，充滿電後可使用19小時。"},{"pid":"ddea426bfd76c8b76e5784ce23ee3c55d019f55d","tid":471871,"uid":141060,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"水果測黎都晒氣  科水買快差牛同線先講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed257791f9fecbd3141f8cdd1a1846b63624c78","tid":471871,"uid":53730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"支那炸彈都幾個<br />\n但LG連測試對象都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa6584479aa7e129458aac77c5682079ea9b14e","tid":471871,"uid":48064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:59:02.000Z","msg":"Iphone用ipad牛差咪快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed80957fe5c83501b03ac364df45823564f1dbb6","tid":471871,"uid":47645,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那炸彈都幾個<br />\n但LG連測試對象都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n消委會表示LG過2個月平2000 到時再測"},{"pid":"e374c9be0c46694522e5d0eb1166f044268fdc0a","tid":471871,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"濕鳩文"},{"pid":"cbc0b8d450ff37995b5513a956a8524a1af16783","tid":471871,"uid":26130,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"Sony Xzp 使撚叉3個鐘<br />\n跟機QC3.0 牛<br />\n平時都係個幾鐘叉完"},{"pid":"8fdfdd75178b9d346afab0cc76d71685a739d3cd","tid":471871,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:13:13.000Z","msg":"宜家d機原裝牛同線叉1個鐘都爆啦"},{"pid":"5a67622e73e28de587cc3aeda571d0cf33bdb592","tid":471871,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:37:57.000Z","msg":"點解one plus  有三個分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad93fc0c9f8a6ac5376402848f73cc544c5732","tid":471871,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:48:02.000Z","msg":"oneplus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa629401a938aa10506bdc385eb5a6c972fc7304","tid":471871,"uid":31475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"之前有